  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Events & Promotions Coordinator (Fun & Easy)",
  "description": "<p>Are you energetic, persuasive, and love talking to people? We're looking for a <strong>Events & Promotions Coordinator </strong> to join our event and brand activation team. If you're looking to build real experience in sales and marketing while working with exciting lifestyle or consumer brands — we want you!</p><p><br /></p><h3><strong>Your Responsibilities:</strong></h3><ul><li>Actively engage with customers at events/pop-ups to promote and <strong>sell products or services</strong></li><li>Communicate brand value clearly and confidently to potential customers</li><li>Support the planning and execution of <strong>event marketing and promotional campaigns</strong></li><li>Assist in setting up booths or displays and ensuring a vibrant brand presence</li><li>Track customer interest, sales figures, and gather feedback for post-event analysis</li><li>Work with the team to brainstorm and implement creative sales tactics</li></ul><h3><strong>Who We’re Looking For:</strong></h3><ul><li>Outgoing, confident, and <strong>sales-driven</strong></li><li>Enjoys meeting people and working in dynamic, energetic environments</li><li>Interest in marketing, brand promotions, or events</li><li>Able to work some evenings/weekends for events</li><li>Bonus: Experience in retail, F&B, or event sales</li><li>Students or fresh grads are welcome to apply!</li></ul><h3><strong>What You’ll Get:</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>Weekly payout</strong> (competitive hourly rates or sales commission — varies by event/project)</li><li>Opportunity to work with top consumer and lifestyle brands</li><li>Real experience in sales, marketing, and customer engagement</li><li>Fun, team-based event environments</li><li>Growth opportunities with recurring project work</li></ul><h3>Apply Now:</h3><p>Send your <strong>resume</strong> and a short intro about yourself to [your email/contact info]. Let us know when you’re available to start — we’ve got events happening!</p>",
